headline: Range Resources (RRC) Beats Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Range Resources (RRC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 6.67% and 5.25%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
